                <h1>Pre-Pasted vs. Peel and Stick Wallpaper: Which One To Choose?</h1>
                <p>Pre-pasted and peel-and-stick wallpaper are popular choices for easy home decorating. Pre-pasted wallpaper requires dampening the back to activate the adhesive, while peel-and-stick can be applied directly without any prep. Both options offer stylish designs, but peel-and-stick is generally easier to remove and reposition, making it perfect for renters.</p>
